  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine whether a DNA chip, designed by Medical Prognosis
      Institute (MPI), can provide an accurate prognosis for survival of NSCLC (adeno-, squamous
      and large cell lung cancer).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
